    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forgotten Cave 是一款 roguelite 地下城爬行游戏，拥有无限的程序生成地下城。收集战利品，找到强力的升级，并在这个神秘的洞穴中尽可能长时间地生存！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/48efe630b358492c9e3669a3cc627b03.avif?t=1772361022\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.poster.avif?t=1772361022\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.webm?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.mp4?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Forgotten Cave</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forgotten Cave 是一款 roguelite 地下城爬行游戏，融合了刺激的动作和探索元素。选择三种独特的职业——战士、弓箭手和法师——每种职业都有自己独特的玩法和能力。深入程序生成的地下城，每次游戏都不同，充满了危险的陷阱、强大的敌人和等待揭开的隐藏秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/b2c1f5b0b9e1f9ebb4af767f918c98b3.avif?t=1772361022\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.poster.avif?t=1772361022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.webm?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.mp4?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏提供了各种各样的战利品和强化道具，能够增强角色的能力，支持多种不同的构建和策略。与具有挑战性的boss战斗，探索传奇的宝藏，努力在不断变化的 Forgotten Cave 深处生存下去。</p>",
